    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
                  <em>
                    This review has been hidden because it contains spoilers. To view it,
                    <a href="#" onclick="Effect.toggle(&#39;reviewTextContainer3992846233&#39;); return false;">click here.</a>
                  </em>
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3992846233" class="readable"
                    style="display:none"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2031632790921329035">Still loving the series! It&apos;s fun to watch Merlin grow into his powers more. It really is a fun world, and it&apos;s fun to discover more about the world with each book. The narrator is still doing a wonderful job. This one took a little bit longer to get moving, but it had more of a sense of mystery to it which was fun. I was really excited about meeting Arthur, and it was fun seeing an old Merlin. </span>
